 Local SEO Strategy<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-55\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#9_Failing_to_Monitor_and_Analyse_SEO_Performance\" >9. Failing to Monitor and Analyse SEO Performance<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-56\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Problem_Making_Decisions_Without_Data_Insights\" >Problem: Making Decisions Without Data Insights<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-57\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Solution_Implement_Comprehensive_SEO_Monitoring\" >Solution: Implement Comprehensive SEO Monitoring<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-58\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Benefit_Data-Driven_Optimisation_for_Sustainable_Growth\" >Benefit: Data-Driven Optimisation for Sustainable Growth<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-59\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Problem_Making_Decisions_Blindly_Without_Data_Insights\" >Problem: Making Decisions Blindly Without Data Insights<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-60\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Solution_Deploy_Comprehensive_SEO_Analytics_Tools\" >Solution: Deploy Comprehensive SEO Analytics Tools<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-61\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Setting_Up_Goals_and_Monitoring_KPIs\" >Setting Up Goals and Monitoring KPIs<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-5' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-62\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Adjusting_Strategies_Based_on_Data\" >Adjusting Strategies Based on Data<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-63\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Benefit_Data-Driven_SEO_Strategy_for_Continuous_Improvement\" >Benefit: Data-Driven SEO Strategy for Continuous Improvement<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-64\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Maximised_ROI_Through_Informed_Decisions\" >Maximised ROI Through Informed Decisions<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-65\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Efficient_Resource_Allocation\" >Efficient Resource Allocation<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-66\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/search-engine-optimisation\/10-seo-mistakes-that-are-killing-your-rankings\/#Adaptation_to_Market_and_Algorithm_Changes\" >Adaptation to Market and Algorithm Changes<\/a><\/li